WEBVTT

00:00:07.560 --> 00:00:09.270
[Kim Kangmin as Choi Siyeol]

00:00:17.360 --> 00:00:19.020
[KEVIN as Na Aejoon]

00:00:24.330 --> 00:00:26.030
[Byunghun as Yeon Jooha]

00:00:32.270 --> 00:00:34.220
[Kim Hongjun as Ji Kyusung]

00:00:41.890 --> 00:00:46.360
[My Bias is Showing?!]

